snippet.textDisplay: Nothing lasts forever. This especially applies to computer programs. Things are constantly changing and if your program is dependent on a chain or programs, then if a single program in the chain changes which would require all the others to update as well and one program in the chain doesn't update then your program is now broken.  It's kind of sad when you get a bit attached to an amusing program or videogame but it breaks at some point and stays broken forever. You would have to move on.
